1. What is the problem you want to solve?
Airbnb is one of the most popular service that is being used worldwide and has gained a lot of momentum in the last few years.
Looking at providing insights to people who want to get into renting their space through airbnb. 

2. Who is your client and why do they care about this problem? In other words, what will your client DO or DECIDE 
based on your analysis that they wouldn’t have otherwise?
Clients will be the space owners. They’ll get an early insights on how they are performing as
compared to other people in the area. They’ll decide weather there is something they
need to change/improve or stop listing their space (waste of money).

3. What data are you going to use for this? How will you acquire this data?
Airbnb listings, Feedback and geolocation data. Data is available on insideairbnb.com

4. In brief, outline your approach to solving this problem (knowing that this might change later).
we’ll proceed with data wrangling first and create a scoring model using nlp (analysing feedback), 
to score each space and predict their likeliness to be rented.

5. What are your deliverables? Typically, this would include code, along with a paper and/or a slide deck.
Code, Slides (Possibly a dashboard)
